{"id":232318703,"title":"#馬拉松 2小時內完成","content":"https://i.imgur.com/5xjoFS9.jpg\n想請教大家在慢跑或是運動時通常藉由什麼方式來激勵自己繼續的動力？\n\n圖文轉自「那些名人教我的事」IG: goodayal15 \n\n——————————\n\n330天前，基普喬蓋在北京大學進行的「飛跑征程」活動後接受了採訪。當時他雖然沒有把話說死，僅僅用的是「可能」來回答問題，但今天，他用行動把「可能」變成了現實。\n\n台北時間10月12日，在奧地利維也納的普拉特公園，基普喬蓋再次向馬拉松人類極限發起衝擊。1小時59分40秒，這是基普喬蓋最終衝過終點線的成績。儘管這個成績不會被國際田聯官方承認，理由是「人為創造的有利條件」，但今後所有人在談論起人類歷史上第一個馬拉松跑進2小時的人時，只會有一個名字被提及——Eliud Kipchoge。","excerpt":"想請教大家在慢跑或是運動時通常藉由什麼方式來激勵自己繼續的動力？圖文轉自「那些名人教我的事」IG： goodayal15，——————————，330天前，基普喬蓋在北京大學進行的「飛跑征程」活動後接","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f4388191-41f8-428d-af69-d07d4481dc9e","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-17T14:08:01.083Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-17T14:08:01.083Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":7,"tags":[],"topics":["運動","慢跑","健身"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"運動","forumAlias":"sport","school":"國立中興大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":7}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/5xjoFS9.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c5d31120-2aef-4d6f-b891-8ffea9daf375","url":"https://i.imgur.com/5xjoFS9l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/5xjoFS9l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/5xjoFS9l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-17T14:08:01.083Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-17T14:08:01.083Z"},{"id":"c5d31120-2aef-4d6f-b891-8ffea9daf375","url":"https://i.imgur.com/5xjoFS9.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/5xjoFS9","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/5xjoFS9l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-17T14:08:01.083Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-17T14:08:01.083Z"}],"postAvatar":""}